Privacy Policy
This android mobile app named DoToDo does not automatically capture any specific personal information from you, (like name, phone number or e-mail address, location), that allows us to identify you individually.

If the android mobile app named DoToDo  requests you to provide personal information, you will be informed for the particular purposes for which the information is gathered e.g. feedback form and adequate security measures will be taken to protect your personal information.

We do not sell or share any personally identifiable information volunteered on the android mobile app named Shishu Aloy Sarathi to any third party (public/private). Any information provided to this android mobile app named Shishu Aloy Sarathi will be protected from loss, misuse, unauthorized access or disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

We gather certain information about the User, such as location coordination of the user for internal use only to show the route direction but not share with 3rd party. and also we do not store the coordination for future use.
